  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IAnalyzer
    Interface for what Analyzers need (minimum).
    IEngine
    Interface for the minimum things an engine needs.
    IQuestion
    Interface for the methods a question needs to have.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractFileManager
    Base class for a FileManager: stores a path.
    CharTree<E>
    Character tree for linking a list of values to a keyword.
    DefaultAnalyzer
    Analyzes stats from a bunch of questions, predicting when the question needs to be asked again based on past performance and the equation: r = e^(-t / s) where r is the percentage the question will be answered correctly, t is time, and s is the weight.
    DefaultEngine
    Default engine that uses command line to get commands.
    DefaultFileManager
    The default file manager that uses the specified path and saves the information to "learnItSaved.txt"
    DefaultQuestion
    Default question that has a specific question and answer.
    Stat
    Stores a time and a value for a question.
    TestDefaultAnalyzer
    Basic test for the DefaultAnalyzer, could be expanded upon.
    TestDefaultQuestion
    Basic tests for the DefaultQuestion, could be expanded upon.
    TestType
    Basic tests for the Type class, could be expanded on.
    TestType.Test1234
    Test class for a basic question.
    Type
    Stores the class name of a class that implements Question.
